# data-models

## Core Entity Models

### Organization Model
- Hierarchical structure with three tiers:
  - Root organization (ACE Engage)
  - Agency organizations
  - Client organizations
- Industry-specific organization profiles
- Multi-tenant data isolation
- Brand configuration and style management

### Campaign Model
- Tracks direct mail marketing initiatives
- Links reward conditions and gift card pools
- Campaign status progression workflow
- Delivery tracking integration

### Gift Card Model
- Pool-based inventory management 
- Provider-specific card activation states
- Balance tracking and reconciliation
- Distribution channel assignment

### Contact Model 
- Lifecycle stages with lead scoring
- Industry-specific profile attributes
- Campaign participation tracking
- Engagement metrics calculation

### Relationships
```
Organization 1:N Campaigns
Campaign 1:N GiftCardPools
Campaign 1:N Conditions
Contact N:M Campaigns
Organization 1:N Contacts
```

## Domain-Specific Types

